videos.description: Deontay Burnett gets the first down but then fumbles and Damon Webb returns it to the 19 yard line.
videos.headline: Burnett fumbles to set up Ohio State in the red zone

videos.description: J.T. Barrett puts the Buckeyes on top in the Cotton Bowl with a 1-yard TD run.
videos.headline: Barrett keeps it himself for score

videos.description: Sam Darnold finds Tyler Vaughns who makes an athletic grab on the sideline for the Trojans.
videos.headline: Vaughns climbs the ladder for great catch

videos.description: On third down the USC defense brings pressure and Uchenna Nwosu takes down J.T. Barrett to end the Buckeye's drive.
videos.headline: USC defense comes up with drive-ending sack

videos.description: Damon Webb picks off Sam Darnold and takes it to the house to extend Ohio State's lead.
videos.headline: Darnold throws a pick-6

videos.description: Sam Darnold rolls out and gets a pass to Deontay Burnett who reaches and after review gets the first down for the Trojans.
videos.headline: Burnett dives for first down to extend drive

videos.description: Tyquan Lewis knocks the ball out of Sam Darnold's hands and the Buckeyes recover for their third forced turnover of the game.
videos.headline: Darnold turns it over again

videos.description: J.T. Barrett runs around the left side straight to the end zone for the touchdown to extend the Buckeye's lead.
videos.headline: Barrett breaks free for 28-yard TD run

videos.description: USC's Michael Pittman Jr. dives for a crazy over-the-shoulder grab.
videos.headline: Pittman Jr. lays out for a wild one-handed catch

videos.description: K.J. Hill loses the ball on the punt and Stephen Carr recovers it for the Trojans giving them a chance to score before halftime.
videos.headline: USC answers with fumble recovery

videos.description: Ronald Jones II strolls in for the score to give USC life late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Jones goes untouched in to the end zone

videos.description: Coach Urban Meyer says his defensive line played well, but his team needs to repeat their performance from the 1st quarter.
videos.headline: Meyer wants his team to get momentum back

videos.description: J.T. Barrett runs for two touchdowns and the Buckeyes defense forces three turnovers in the first half as Ohio State leads USC 24-7.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Barrett, OSU in command at the half) 2017/12/29 ESHEET SOTFFULL

videos.headline: Barrett, OSU in command at the half

videos.description: Sam Darnold is sacked by Sam Hubbard and USC is forced to punt.
videos.headline: Buckeyes defense continues to get to Darnold

videos.description: Sam Darnold goes deep to Tyler Vaughns who hauls in the 37-yard pass and stays in bounds and after review it remains a catch.
videos.headline: Vaughns makes sweet sideline catch

videos.description: USC's Chase McGrath misses the 28-yard field goal off the upright.
videos.headline: McGrath doinks it off the upright

videos.description: J.T. Barrett completes a 20-yard pass to Marcus Baugh breaking Drew Brees' record for total offense in Big 10 history.
videos.headline: Barrett passes Drew Brees in Big 10 record books

videos.description: USC's Tyler Vaughns dives and gets a foot down for a 30-yard grab.
videos.headline: Vaughns hauls in great catch on the sideline

videos.description: Jalyn Holmes tackles Sam Darnold from behind, forcing him to fumble, and Robert Landers recovers it for the Buckeyes.
videos.headline: Darnold turns the ball over again vs. Ohio State

videos.description: Sam Darnold runs out of bounds and there is a late push sparking a large shoving match between both teams.
videos.headline: Sideline scuffle ensues after a late push

videos.description: Urban Meyer says he is proud of J.T. Barrett and his senior class and that his defensive line was key in disrupting Sam Darnold.
videos.headline: Meyer calls Barrett an Ohio State legend

videos.description: The Buckeyes' defense and special teams were dominant against USC sealing their 24-7 victory.
videos.headline: Ohio State's defense was key in Cotton Bowl win vs. USC

videos.description: J.T. Barrett says that he is thankful to be a part of this team and gives credit to his teammates for the Buckeyes' success this season.
videos.headline: Barrett thankful to be a part of Cotton Bowl victory

videos.description: J.T. Barrett runs for two touchdowns while Sam Darnold is sacked eight times as Ohio State defeats USC 24-7.

videos.headline: Barrett, OSU cruise to Cotton Bowl win

videos.description: Kirk Herbstreit joins SVP and breaks down the Ohio State-USC game and how Urban Meyer did a great job getting his team ready.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Herbstreit gives Meyer a lot of credit) 2107/12/30 SVP

videos.headline: Herbstreit gives Meyer a lot of credit

videos.description: USC's playcaller Sam Darnold failed to throw a touchdown against Ohio State, and now contemplates his NFL future.
videos.headline: Darnold reflects on Cotton Bowl loss

videos.description: Ohio State forces four USC turnovers and J.T. Barrett rushes for two touchdowns as the Buckeyes top the Trojans 24-7 to win the Goodyear Cotton Bowl Classic.
videos.headline: Buckeyes capitalize on Trojans' struggles for 24-7 win

videos.description: Ohio State stifled Sam Darnold and the Trojans, forcing four turnovers in a 24-7 Buckeyes victory.
